doctype html
html(lang="en")
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    meta(name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
    title Behold
    link(rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/public/stars.png")
    style.
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background: url('/public/42.gif') no-repeat center center fixed;
        background-size: cover;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        height: 100vh;
        margin: 0;
      }
      .home-container {
        background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
        padding: 2rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 600px;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        text-align: center;
      }
      h1 {
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      p {
        color: #555;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }
      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 4px;
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 1rem;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .btn:hover {
        background-color: #0056b3;
      }
  body
    .home-container
      h1 Welcome
      p After an exhausting trip, it's time to meet your destiny. Forget what you know, for it will not serve you where you're heading. 
      p We all have struggled enough, fighting to keep our heads where they are.
      p Ours will not be hunted anymore. Let go of your mind.  
      a.btn(href="/awaken") I am ready
